# Student Grade Tracker GUI

This is a simple Java Swing project made by **Dhiraj Kumar (MCA – SIOM Pune)** for CodeAlpha internship tasks.

## Features

* Add student name and marks
* View students in table
* Show report (average, highest, lowest)
* Show list of student names

## Technology Used

* Java
* Swing GUI
* VS Code

## How to Run

1. Open in VS Code
2. Run commands:

javac StudentGradeTrackerGUI.java
java StudentGradeTrackerGUI

